our personalities

16:05.632 --> 16:07.801
in some idyllic afterlife.

16:07.884 --> 16:10.720
We all pray for some miracle,

16:10.804 --> 16:14.432
some drug, potion, pill.

16:20.230 --> 16:25.151
Perhaps, though,
it takes something else.

16:25.235 --> 16:29.698
