16:37.664 --> 16:41.876
We will discuss the location of the will
in the brain structure

16:42.002 --> 16:45.296
at another time.

16:45.380 --> 16:47.465
Mr. West!

16:47.549 --> 16:50.885
I suggest you get
yourself a pen!

16:52.721 --> 16:54.139
Class dismissed.

16:56.641 --> 16:58.226
How can you teach such drivel?

16:58.309 --> 17:00.270
These people are here to learn
and you're closing their minds

17:00.353 --> 17:01.521
before they even have a chance!

17:01.604 --> 17:03.023
What are you here for,
Mr. West?

17:03.064 --> 17:05.025
You know, you should have
stolen more of Gruber's ideas,

17:05.066 --> 17:06.443
then at least you'd have ideas!

17:06.526 --> 17:08.528
Mr. West!

17:11.281 --> 17:14.159
It is going to be
a pleasure to fail you.

17:21.374 --> 17:25.377
I would like to propose a toast

17:25.462 --> 17:27.589
to the National Science Foundation

17:27.672 --> 17:31.926
for recognizing the genius
of Dr. Carl Hill,

17:32.927 --> 17:36.056
and for awarding
Miskatonic Medical School

17:36.097 --> 17:37.682
its largest grant ever.

17:39.059 --> 17:43.229
Your new laser drill is going
to revolutionize neurosurgery.

17:43.313 --> 17:47.942
To the foundation,
and to Miskatonic.

17:51.321 --> 17:52.864
It's all right, sweetheart,
you can drink up.

17:52.947 --> 17:53.990
We're celebrating.

17:54.074 --> 17:56.159
I know, Daddy,
but I have to go soon.

17:56.242 --> 17:59.954
After preparing such a feast,
you must be tired.

18:00.080 --> 18:01.706
I have a study date.

18:01.790 --> 18:03.166
With Daniel?

18:03.249 --> 18:04.834
Yeah.

18:04.918 --> 18:06.169
Daniel Cain'?

18:07.629 --> 18:10.632
Herbert West has moved in
with him, hasn't he?

18:10.715 --> 18:12.383
