18:19.599 --> 18:22.435
So, your daughter
is seeing Cain, eh?

18:24.270 --> 18:27.273
You think that's wise, Alan'?

18:27.357 --> 18:28.483
Dan!

18:28.566 --> 18:30.235
Hello, sir.

18:30.318 --> 18:31.945
Dr. Hill.

18:32.028 --> 18:33.988
Would you join us
for a glass of wine?

18:35.865 --> 18:37.742
Actually, we have some
work to do.

18:37.826 --> 18:39.285
Why don't you study here?

18:39.369 --> 18:42.789
Well, I've her home soon,
don't worry.

18:42.872 --> 18:47.127
Well then, one last toast?

18:48.711 --> 18:50.547
To Megan...

18:50.630 --> 18:54.676
my esteemed colleague's capable,

18:54.759 --> 18:58.263
beautiful, loving daughter,

18:58.346 --> 19:01.474
the obsession of all
who fall under her spell.

19:17.323 --> 19:19.325
Dan.

19:19.409 --> 19:21.870
No.

19:21.953 --> 19:24.664
Please!

19:24.747 --> 19:25.832
Okay, what is it?

19:25.915 --> 19:27.792
I don't know, it's...

19:27.876 --> 19:31.045
Look, it's not you, really.

19:31.171 --> 19:33.298
It's just a lot of little things.

19:33.381 --> 19:35.049
Like what?

19:35.175 --> 19:37.719
Well, West is always in his room
with the door closed.

19:37.802 --> 19:39.762
I mean, do you ever see him?

19:39.846 --> 19:41.347
Does he ever eat?

19:41.431 --> 19:43.975
I told you, he's a little cracked.

19:45.810 --> 19:48.646
He bothers you, too.

19:48.730 --> 19:50.857
No, don't be ridiculous.

19:50.940 --> 19:52.525
Rufus is terrified of him.

19:52.609 --> 19:54.068
When West comes in,
he runs and hides.

19:54.194 --> 19:55.987
Rufus hides
and runs all the time,

19:56.070 --> 19:57.363
it's standard cat activity.

19:57.447 --> 19:58.448
Yes, but not when we're together,

19:58.531 --> 20:00.491
then he's all over us trying
to get your attention and...

20:01.993 --> 20:03.578
Where is he?

20:03.661 --> 20:05.079
I haven't seen him
since we got here.

20:05.205 --> 20:06.372
It's okay, he's around here.

20:06.456 --> 20:07.457
I haven't even heard him,

20:07.540 --> 20:10.210
usually he at least knocks
something over when I'm here.

20:12.629 --> 20:14.756
