20:16.466 --> 20:19.260
Rufus... Rufus... Rufus.

20:19.344 --> 20:20.470
Pss pss pss pss.

20:20.553 --> 20:24.057
Come on, you fat cat.

20:24.140 --> 20:25.600
Here, kitty!

20:25.683 --> 20:27.393
Rufus.

20:27.477 --> 20:29.812
Come on now, you mad animal.

20:29.896 --> 20:31.856
Don't you try to hide from me.

20:31.940 --> 20:34.400
I know all of your tricks.

20:34.484 --> 20:37.403
Rufus? Where are you, boy?

20:37.487 --> 20:39.405
Here, kitty.

20:39.489 --> 20:41.532
