21:05.098 --> 21:07.725
Rufus?

21:11.271 --> 21:14.023
Rufus?

21:15.984 --> 21:17.819
Rufus.

21:23.741 --> 21:26.494
Rufus?

21:34.335 --> 21:35.420
Hey, boy.

21:42.552 --> 21:44.637
Rufus, are you in here?

21:49.684 --> 21:52.520
Here, boy.

21:52.603 --> 21:54.564
Here, kitty.

22:07.201 --> 22:10.538
Rufus?

22:15.668 --> 22:18.129
Oh, Dan, I think it's...

