What's the matter?

22:25.345 --> 22:27.889
I thought I was renting
a private room, Dan!

22:27.972 --> 22:29.140
Meg, what the hell
are you doing in here?

22:29.223 --> 22:31.100
- I...
- Would you please leave, now!

22:31.184 --> 22:33.353
Easy!

22:33.436 --> 22:34.645
In the fridge.

22:44.947 --> 22:46.699
I was going to show you.

22:46.783 --> 22:48.785
Shut up.

22:53.831 --> 22:55.541
What happened?

22:55.625 --> 22:58.669
It was dead when I found it.

22:58.753 --> 23:00.755
You killed him.

23:00.838 --> 23:02.548
He hated you!

23:02.632 --> 23:05.426
Meg. It suffocated.

23:08.846 --> 23:12.558
It knocked the garbage over and
it got its head stuck in a jar.

23:12.642 --> 23:14.560
You weren't home,
so I put it in there.

23:14.644 --> 23:16.270
I certainly didn't think
you'd want to find it like that.

23:16.396 --> 23:18.189
I didn't want
to stink the place up.

23:18.272 --> 23:20.233
I was going to show you.

23:20.316 --> 23:21.901
You couldn't call, or write a note?

23:21.984 --> 23:24.028
I was busy pushing bodies around,
as you well know,

23:24.112 --> 23:25.405
and what would a note say, Dan?

23:25.446 --> 23:27.907
"Cat dead, details later"?

23:27.990 --> 23:29.033
I knew you were fond of it.

23:29.117 --> 23:30.284
You killed him, I know you did.

23:30.410 --> 23:31.285
He killed him.

23:31.411 --> 23:32.912
Besides, I do not
like people in my room!

23:32.995 --> 23:35.665
All right, that's enough.

23:42.588 --> 23:44.257
I think you both better leave, now.

23:44.340 --> 23:45.341
What the hell is this?

23:45.425 --> 23:46.551
That is none of your business.

23:46.634 --> 23:47.677
Yeah, I think it is my business!

23:47.760 --> 23:48.803
Just as it is none of my business

23:48.886 --> 23:50.513
that you're sleeping
with Dean Halsey's daughter.

23:54.058 --> 23:55.601
You know, I would not want
to see a fellow student,

23:55.685 --> 23:57.437
especially one
as promising as yourself,

23:57.478 --> 23:59.814
be thrown out of school,
out of the profession...

23:59.897 --> 24:03.443
on moral ground.

24:03.484 --> 24:05.570
I think Dr. Halsey
just might understand.

24:05.653 --> 24:07.321
Oh, do you?

24:07.447 --> 24:09.866
Well, you may well be right.

24:09.949 --> 24:13.703
Are you sure you want
to find out?

24:59.123 --> 25:00.333
Herbert?

25:01.334 --> 25:02.502
Herbert.

