27:30.983 --> 27:33.819
All life is a physical
and chemical process, correct?

27:33.903 --> 27:37.865
It stands to reason then, that if one
could find extremely fresh specimens

27:37.948 --> 27:41.369
and recharge that chemical process,
bang, we have re-animation.

27:41.452 --> 27:46.040
- The theory is not new, West.
- But my reagent is.

27:46.123 --> 27:47.708
Read.

27:52.922 --> 27:54.590
"With various animating solutions,"

27:54.674 --> 27:56.384
"I have killed and brought
to animated life,"

27:56.467 --> 28:00.304
"a number of rabbits,
guinea pigs, cats, and dogs."

28:00.388 --> 28:02.556
I've broken the 6 to 12 minute barrier.

28:02.682 --> 28:04.517
I've conquered brain death.

28:06.936 --> 28:08.979
"With the higher animals
and the consequent"

28:09.063 --> 28:13.859
increased strength of solution,
reaction has become more violent...

28:13.943 --> 28:17.029
and my research
has become more difficult.

28:17.113 --> 28:20.449
Which is why
I need you to help me.

28:20.533 --> 28:21.534
Help you?

28:21.617 --> 28:23.869
You are the perfect person
to assist me.

28:23.953 --> 28:26.872
You're hard-working, bright,
people respect you,

28:26.956 --> 28:31.544
and you have access
to certain authorities.

28:31.627 --> 28:35.172
We can defeat death.

28:35.256 --> 28:37.842
We can achieve
every doctor's dream.

28:37.925 --> 28:41.470
You'll be famous... and live lifetimes.

28:41.554 --> 28:44.932
You haven't done this on people?

28:49.395 --> 28:51.605
I've done all I can here.

28:51.731 --> 28:54.942
I'll need new lab space.

28:55.025 --> 28:56.944
You will help me.

28:57.027 --> 28:59.655
- No!
- Why? Because it's mad?

28:59.739 --> 29:01.365
No, because I don't
believe you.

29:01.449 --> 29:03.367
How can you say that?
You've seen the results.

29:03.451 --> 29:05.661
No, Rufus wasn't dead
to begin with.

29:05.745 --> 29:07.413
You drugged him
and reduced his vital signs.

29:07.496 --> 29:08.622
You lowered his body temperature.

29:08.748 --> 29:09.832
He couldn't have been dead.

29:09.915 --> 29:11.500
Do you agree
that he's dead now?

29:12.585 --> 29:14.754
Do you agree
that he's dead now?

29:22.511 --> 29:24.513
West, no!

29:29.018 --> 29:30.227
West, stop!

29:30.311 --> 29:32.354
I'll show you.

29:32.438 --> 29:34.148
- Then you'll help me.
- No!

29:34.231 --> 29:35.357
Yes, you will.

29:35.441 --> 29:39.028
That is why I brought the infernal beast
back to life in the first place.

29:44.825 --> 29:46.660
- In the brain?
- Of course.

29:50.831 --> 29:54.710
Don't expect it to tango,
it has a broken back.

29:59.340 --> 30:03.969
God! Why does
it make that noise?

30:04.053 --> 30:06.639
Birth is always painful.

30:11.393 --> 30:12.937
It was dead.

30:13.020 --> 30:14.396
Twice.

30:18.067 --> 30:19.985
- Oh, it's him!
- Baby, what are you doing here?

30:20.069 --> 30:21.821
It's Rufus! HOW did...

30:21.862 --> 30:24.657
- Come on, let's go upstairs.
- Oh! Oh, my god.

30:32.456 --> 30:36.752
Herbert West has effected
re-animation in dead animal tissue.

30:39.255 --> 30:43.008
Mr. Cain, I'm surprised.

30:43.092 --> 30:44.093
No, I've seen it.

30:44.176 --> 30:48.097
He brought back a dead animal,
a cat, back to life.

30:48.180 --> 30:51.183
I hadn't expected such nonsense
from you, Mr. Cain,

30:51.267 --> 30:54.144
but I should have guessed it
when you took up with Mr. West.

30:54.228 --> 30:57.773
I know he's unstable,
but I've seen the results,

30:57.857 --> 31:00.025
and so has your daughter.

31:00.109 --> 31:02.194
What have you been doing
with my daughter?

31:02.278 --> 31:04.613
She walked into an experiment.

31:04.697 --> 31:07.783
You've involved Megan
in your insanity?

31:07.867 --> 31:09.785
I never intended to involve her.

31:09.869 --> 31:12.746
Tomorrow morning, you will
submit to me a written apology

31:12.872 --> 31:14.540
for this entire affair.

31:14.623 --> 31:18.002
These experiments were clearly beyond
the scope of your legitimate studies.

31:18.085 --> 31:21.422
They've obviously interfered with
your ability to do your class work.

31:21.505 --> 31:26.051
If any equipment from the hospital
or from the laboratories

31:26.135 --> 31:29.638
of Miskatonic University were involved
in any of this unauthorized activity,

31:29.722 --> 31:31.599
criminal charges
may be pressed.

31:31.682 --> 31:35.311
You will, in any case, have
your student loan rescinded.

31:37.563 --> 31:40.399
My loan?

31:40.482 --> 31:42.776
I won't be able to continue school.

31:42.902 --> 31:45.321
As for Mr. West,
he needs submit no apology.

31:45.404 --> 31:48.782
You may tell him that he may
continue with his research

31:48.908 --> 31:51.076
without the impediment
of an education.

31:51.160 --> 31:53.954
As of now, he is no longer
a student of this university.

31:55.414 --> 31:57.082
Sir, can we please just discuss this?

31:57.166 --> 31:59.418
I think you're being blinded
by your emotions.

32:00.461 --> 32:03.047
That will be all, Mr. Cain.

32:11.639 --> 32:13.557
Don't take this out on Meg.

32:14.600 --> 32:16.101
She tried to stop me.

32:16.185 --> 32:19.188
I said that will be all.

32:34.954 --> 32:37.373
- Oh, they keep on a comin', don't they?
- Oh, yeah.

32:46.840 --> 32:49.677
You ain't got my lunch
under there, have you?

32:49.760 --> 32:52.012
Yeah, one meatball
run over by a semi.

32:52.096 --> 32:53.472
Ew!

32:53.555 --> 32:55.849
I lost my appetite. You gonna
be around for a while?

32:55.975 --> 32:58.477
I might go catch me
some coffee.

32:58.560 --> 33:00.062
- Take your time.
- You got it.

33:09.279 --> 33:11.031
Meatball?

33:11.115 --> 33:12.992
Just put your shoes on.

33:25.921 --> 33:27.339
Oh, damn, if we get caught...

33:27.423 --> 33:29.341
Oh, well, what will they do?

33:29.425 --> 33:31.176
Embalm us?

33:31.260 --> 33:33.762
Let's go.

33:51.947 --> 33:54.575
Burn victim.

33:59.163 --> 34:01.165
- Here's your meatball.
- Oh.

34:05.919 --> 34:08.047
Shotgun wound to the head.

34:10.215 --> 34:12.217
Oh, god, he's rotten.

34:14.887 --> 34:17.056
- Malpractice.
- Shit.

34:18.264 --> 34:20.059
Let's go, we're not going
to find anything.

34:20.141 --> 34:21.851
Wait. Wait!

34:26.690 --> 34:29.525
Yes, I think you.

34:29.610 --> 34:31.360
How long?

34:31.445 --> 34:33.781
He arrived early this evening.

34:33.864 --> 34:36.199
John Doe, apparently just dropped dead.

34:36.283 --> 34:39.078
No record of any damage.
It's almost perfect.

34:40.329 --> 34:41.789
Why "almost"?

34:41.871 --> 34:43.873
Could be heart damage.

34:43.956 --> 34:44.958
Then let's just find another one.

34:45.083 --> 34:47.085
No! We do not have time!

34:47.168 --> 34:49.004
All we need tonight

34:49.088 --> 34:51.507
is a specific, conscious reaction.

34:51.590 --> 34:53.175
He's been dead for hours.

34:53.257 --> 34:56.553
Any evidence of re-animated
consciousness will justify proceeding.

34:59.181 --> 35:01.183
Start the recorder.

35:02.267 --> 35:04.269
Start the damn recorder!

35:07.523 --> 35:09.525
Make the entry.

35:11.360 --> 35:13.278
October...

35:13.362 --> 35:15.405
Tenth.

35:15.489 --> 35:17.950
- Subject: Male.
- Age?

35:19.034 --> 35:22.204
Age, early twenties.

35:22.287 --> 35:25.290
- Physical condition?
- No deformities.

35:25.374 --> 35:29.002
Appears to have been in
excellent physical condition.

35:31.338 --> 35:34.133
Apparent cause of death...

35:36.844 --> 35:38.846
what?

35:38.929 --> 35:43.517
Heart failure.

35:45.727 --> 35:48.939
Time, 10:33 PM.

35:49.022 --> 35:51.859
10:33 PM.

35:54.486 --> 35:56.488
15 cc's.

35:58.532 --> 36:00.993
15 cc's of reagent being administered.

36:09.501 --> 36:11.295
He loves me,
we're getting married.

36:11.378 --> 36:14.256
He's mad! I've seen this happen
to medical students before.

36:14.339 --> 36:15.757
Good ones!

36:15.841 --> 36:19.094
Dr. Harrod, is Mr. Cain loose
in this hospital?

36:19.178 --> 36:21.096
In the morgue, I think, doctor.

36:21.180 --> 36:24.099
I specifically told
Dr. Riley to suspend him,

36:24.183 --> 36:27.102
and to take him off the floor
if he reported to work!

36:27.186 --> 36:30.606
Dr. Riley's been
in emergency surgery for four hours.

36:30.689 --> 36:33.984
I haven't seen him.

36:34.067 --> 36:35.360
Time elapsed.

36:39.198 --> 36:41.074
15 seconds.

36:43.368 --> 36:46.121
Something should
have happened by now.

36:57.216 --> 37:00.302
It's not working.

37:00.385 --> 37:01.386
Let's get out of here!

37:01.470 --> 37:04.640
Obviously, the human dosage
factor is unknown.

37:04.723 --> 37:07.351
Increasing the dosage,
20 cc's of reagent.

37:07.434 --> 37:09.269
- Herbert, let's go!
- No!

37:35.170 --> 37:36.421
Damn!

37:36.505 --> 37:39.508
Page Mr. Cain and have him report
to Level L security desk,

37:39.591 --> 37:42.719
and make sure
that she stays right here.

37:42.803 --> 37:45.264
You can't stop me! I followed you here,
and I'm gonna follow you

37:45.305 --> 37:46.431
- until you listen to me!
- Megan!

37:46.515 --> 37:47.516
- I love him!
- You're my daughter,

37:47.599 --> 37:49.434
and you'll do as you're told!

37:49.518 --> 37:51.436
Sit down, Miss Halsey.

37:51.520 --> 37:53.981
Mr. Cain will be up soon,
you can discuss it then.

37:54.064 --> 37:55.899
Don't blame him, Daddy!

37:55.983 --> 37:58.986
We failed.

37:59.069 --> 38:00.279
Come on, let's go!

38:00.320 --> 38:01.863
I mean, someone
could be coming any minute!

38:01.947 --> 38:05.367
He failed! Not I!

38:05.450 --> 38:07.661
<i>Mr. Cain, Mr. Daniel Cain,</i>

38:07.744 --> 38:10.831
<i>please report
to the security desk, Level L</i>

38:11.832 --> 38:13.125
Oh, god.

38:13.208 --> 38:14.876
Cover him up.

38:16.003 --> 38:18.422
- Let's go!
- All right!

38:37.149 --> 38:39.568
Grab him!

38:43.113 --> 38:44.781
Stop!

38:48.702 --> 38:50.078
It listened to me.

38:58.962 --> 39:00.547
Cain?

39:02.591 --> 39:04.384
Cain?

39:06.636 --> 39:08.555
Cain, open up this door.

39:09.556 --> 39:12.642
Help!

39:12.726 --> 39:14.061
Get help!

39:14.144 --> 39:16.980
Is West in there with you?

39:17.064 --> 39:18.231
You're in a lot of trouble,
both of you!

39:41.671 --> 39:43.465
No!

39:50.639 --> 39:52.641
Let go!

40:05.654 --> 40:07.406
Stop!

40:07.489 --> 40:08.657
For god's sakes!

40:09.658 --> 40:12.744
Dan... look out.

40:42.691 --> 40:45.610
Come on.

40:45.694 --> 40:47.696
Find the recorder.

40:49.281 --> 40:52.242
- Herbert... no.
- Did you see him react?

40:52.325 --> 40:54.911
He listened to me.
It made a conscious act.

40:54.995 --> 40:57.914
He heard you as an animal would.

40:58.915 --> 41:01.001
Herbert, no, you can't be serious!

41:01.084 --> 41:02.544
Hell, you may be right.

41:02.627 --> 41:03.753
It'd probably been dead too long.

41:03.837 --> 41:06.465
It wasn't fresh enough!

41:06.506 --> 41:09.468
We probably only revived the senses
and the instincts, so, come on!

41:09.509 --> 41:11.636
Help me get him up.

41:11.720 --> 41:12.804
Is he dead?

41:12.888 --> 41:15.223
Of course, will you
give me a hand here?

41:15.307 --> 41:17.767
Now, he interrupted an important
experiment in progress.

41:17.851 --> 41:19.186
Granted, it was an accident.

41:19.269 --> 41:21.646
But this is the freshest body
that we could come across

41:21.730 --> 41:22.898
save of killing one ourselves,

41:22.981 --> 41:25.317
and every moment that we spend
talking about it costs us results!

41:25.400 --> 41:27.402
Now will you give me a hand?

41:29.362 --> 41:33.074
Dan, we can bring him back to life.

41:46.713 --> 41:48.298
Okay.

41:56.139 --> 41:58.266
Now, get the recorder.

41:59.726 --> 42:01.228
Find my serum.

42:04.940 --> 42:06.816
This is a dream.

42:06.900 --> 42:08.985
Fiction.

42:09.986 --> 42:11.780
Here. Do his other hand.

42:13.907 --> 42:16.451
Oh, good.

42:16.535 --> 42:22.332
Unbreakable plastic, one of
man's few durable inventions.

42:24.417 --> 42:26.419
Certainly more durable than this.

42:27.546 --> 42:31.341
We need you in the crash room.

42:31.424 --> 42:33.301
Coming.

43:02.122 --> 43:04.165
12 cc's being administered.

43:04.249 --> 43:08.837
The dosage lessened in accordance
to the freshness of the subject.

43:22.851 --> 43:28.315
5 seconds.

43:28.398 --> 43:30.650
Come on.

43:30.734 --> 43:34.446
I'll show you.

43:34.529 --> 43:38.617
15 seconds. I'll show you!

43:38.658 --> 43:40.160
17 seconds.

43:40.243 --> 43:42.662
Re-animation at 17 seconds!
The eyes opened!

43:42.746 --> 43:44.956
Doctor. Dr. Halsey,

43:45.040 --> 43:48.627
you once did me a favor by
letting me into your medical school.

43:48.668 --> 43:49.794
Doctor?

43:49.878 --> 43:51.630
Welcome back to life.

44:14.944 --> 44:16.821
Daddy?

44:16.905 --> 44:18.531
Dan?

44:18.657 --> 44:20.075
Damn the bitch.

44:20.158 --> 44:23.828
Megan... Meg?

44:25.705 --> 44:30.377
Dan, what is it,
are you all right?

44:34.297 --> 44:38.927
Dan, he's trying to speak,
the recorder!

44:41.596 --> 44:43.056
No!

44:43.139 --> 44:44.933
Daddy!

44:45.016 --> 44:46.101
Daddy, no!

44:46.184 --> 44:47.894
No! No, Meg, don't go near him!

44:47.977 --> 44:48.895
What the hell happened here?

44:48.978 --> 44:50.855
Dan, you all right?

44:50.939 --> 44:52.732
Who's that?

44:54.693 --> 44:58.571
That is Dean Halsey, sir.

44:58.697 --> 45:01.700
You see I came down here
to visit Mr. Cain,

45:01.741 --> 45:04.703
who was here working
and Halsey entered

45:04.786 --> 45:07.706
and started ranting at us,
rather irrationally.

45:07.789 --> 45:09.207
No!

45:09.290 --> 45:11.751
He was just angry!

45:11.835 --> 45:12.794
Daddy!

45:12.877 --> 45:13.837
Meg. What happened?

45:13.920 --> 45:15.004
Who's that over there?

45:15.088 --> 45:16.881
Just a corpse.

45:16.965 --> 45:20.385
You see, Halsey came in,
grabbed that thing,

45:20.468 --> 45:23.763
and, well, went crazy.

45:23.847 --> 45:25.265
Dean Halsey?

45:25.348 --> 45:26.307
Dean Halsey!

45:26.391 --> 45:27.308
Arrest them!

45:27.392 --> 45:29.185
I'm calling the police!

45:29.269 --> 45:30.979
Oh, Daddy!

45:42.991 --> 45:47.579
Shock... don't worry.

46:13.229 --> 46:16.691
Daddy.

46:16.775 --> 46:19.235
He can't hear you, or see you.

46:19.319 --> 46:23.948
That's a one-way mirror.

46:24.032 --> 46:28.036
What is wrong with him, Doctor?

46:28.119 --> 46:29.204
Will he ever be...

46:29.287 --> 46:31.956
Until we know exactly what
happened to him,

46:32.040 --> 46:37.796
there's no way to determine
his course of recovery.

46:37.837 --> 46:40.590
That's why I need you
to sign a release,

46:40.673 --> 46:44.803
so that I can perform
exploratory surgery on him.

46:44.844 --> 46:47.806
Is that absolutely necessary,
Dr. Hill?

46:47.847 --> 46:52.519
I know how difficult
this must be for you,

46:52.602 --> 46:57.816
but I'm convinced that your father's
problem is neurological.

46:57.857 --> 47:01.069
Of course, we'll take
every precaution.

47:04.614 --> 47:07.992
You must trust me.

47:19.337 --> 47:23.049
I want to take a look at the
right frontal lobe.

47:23.132 --> 47:25.009
I'll open the skull here...

47:25.093 --> 47:28.012
I don't want to know.

47:28.096 --> 47:31.349
Just help him.

47:52.245 --> 47:55.039
Please, doctor.

47:55.123 --> 47:58.126
Please let me talk to him.

47:58.209 --> 48:00.795
No.

48:00.879 --> 48:05.091
I must insist you leave his
treatment up to me.

48:05.174 --> 48:10.346
I want you to think of me as someone
you can come to with your problems.

48:13.558 --> 48:16.895
Or if you're ever lonely.

48:20.523 --> 48:24.402
I know you're all by yourself now.

48:33.244 --> 48:35.622
I'm going to take care
of him, doctor,

48:35.705 --> 48:39.167
and I'm going to find out
what happened to him.

49:20.333 --> 49:22.710
What are you doing here?

49:22.794 --> 49:25.296
I've been waiting for you.

49:25.380 --> 49:29.467
I have to tell you.

49:29.550 --> 49:33.888
What did you do to him?

49:33.972 --> 49:38.518
What did you and West do
to him to make him like that?

49:38.601 --> 49:42.981
It was... it was horrible.

49:43.022 --> 49:46.567
I didn't...

49:46.651 --> 49:49.028
What did you do to him?

49:56.119 --> 49:57.662
He's not insane.

50:02.166 --> 50:05.169
He's dead.

50:05.253 --> 50:09.549
No. No.

50:09.632 --> 50:13.136
You're insane,
you are insane, no!

50:13.219 --> 50:15.179
You know it's true, Meg.

50:15.263 --> 50:16.806
You know it's true.

50:16.889 --> 50:20.018
No.

50:23.438 --> 50:29.027
Daddy. Daddy.

50:32.572 --> 50:36.034
I'll tell you, Meg, everything.

50:48.337 --> 50:50.798
Good evening, Mr. West.

50:55.553 --> 50:57.805
What do you want?

50:57.889 --> 51:00.892
I want to know why Halsey's
heart fibrillated.

51:00.975 --> 51:02.310
I don't have to talk to you.

51:02.393 --> 51:04.062
Why his pulse is erratic.

51:04.145 --> 51:06.230
I've told everything I know
to the police.

51:06.314 --> 51:08.566
Why he cries out in pain.

51:08.649 --> 51:10.068
You can leave now, doctor.

51:10.109 --> 51:14.864
When we both know
he is quite dead.

51:21.329 --> 51:25.083
Interesting little laboratory
you have here.

51:25.124 --> 51:30.463
Mr. West, I recognize this?

51:32.715 --> 51:34.634
What do you want?

51:34.717 --> 51:38.846
Yes, we are both scientists.

51:38.930 --> 51:41.891
Let us get to the point.

51:45.353 --> 51:49.107
I want your discovery.

51:49.190 --> 51:52.985
Whatever it is that gives the
dead the appearance of life.

51:53.111 --> 51:55.279
Oh, it is not the appearance
of life, it is life.

51:55.363 --> 51:59.617
This is not magic, as you say,
I am a scientist.

51:59.700 --> 52:03.204
I'll have you locked up
for a madman...

52:03.287 --> 52:05.373
or a murderer.

52:11.379 --> 52:14.632
You will do...

52:14.715 --> 52:17.385
what I tell you to do.

52:50.626 --> 52:53.921
Ingenious, Mr. West.

52:54.005 --> 52:59.260
Your extension of that old fool
Gruber's work is really quite...

52:59.343 --> 53:00.386
brilliant.

53:21.199 --> 53:22.992
Has Dr. Hill examined
your father?

53:23.075 --> 53:24.368
Yes.

53:24.452 --> 53:28.080
He wanted to do exploratory
surgery on him.

53:28.206 --> 53:30.416
Oh, shit.

53:30.499 --> 53:33.628
Then he'll find out.

53:33.711 --> 53:36.881
Eventually he'll find out.

53:36.964 --> 53:39.926
Let us see...

53:40.009 --> 53:43.387
my new serum at work?

53:46.349 --> 53:48.267
Dead cat tissue.

53:53.231 --> 53:57.276
Reagent.

54:20.299 --> 54:22.510
Magnificent.

54:40.486 --> 54:43.906
Yes, Mr. West.

54:43.990 --> 54:48.452
I will be famous.

54:59.422 --> 55:01.924
Laid to rest.

55:47.762 --> 55:50.598
Yes.

55:54.268 --> 55:57.104
Parts.

55:57.188 --> 56:02.360
I've never done whole parts.

56:51.909 --> 56:56.664
Wesssssst

56:59.834 --> 57:01.919
Yes, doctor.

57:02.002 --> 57:04.588
It's Herbert West.

57:04.672 --> 57:05.840
What are you thinking?

57:05.923 --> 57:09.844
How do you feel?

57:09.927 --> 57:13.431
Yooooooou.

57:13.472 --> 57:14.598
" You."

57:14.682 --> 57:20.438
Baaassstaaard

58:57.201 --> 58:58.285
Dan!

58:58.369 --> 59:01.580
Oh my god, what has Hill
done to him?

59:06.794 --> 59:11.090
Looks like a laser drill.

59:11.173 --> 59:12.800
Your father's been lobotomized.

59:58.345 --> 01:00:01.599
That's it.

01:00:01.682 --> 01:00:04.852
My work! My work!

01:00:04.935 --> 01:00:05.894
What's going on?

01:00:05.978 --> 01:00:08.731
My work is gone.

01:00:08.814 --> 01:00:10.774
It's all gone.

01:00:10.858 --> 01:00:12.359
He took my serum!

01:00:12.443 --> 01:00:13.777
Except for what
I have upstairs.

01:00:13.861 --> 01:00:15.279
Who?

01:00:15.362 --> 01:00:16.697
What happened here?

01:00:16.780 --> 01:00:18.157
Hill.

01:00:18.240 --> 01:00:21.201
Hill took my serum!
My notes! Everything.

01:00:21.285 --> 01:00:22.286
Herbert, you're insane!

01:00:22.369 --> 01:00:24.538
- Now, what happened here?
- I had to kill him.

01:00:24.622 --> 01:00:26.790
What?

01:00:26.874 --> 01:00:30.628
He's dead?

01:00:30.711 --> 01:00:34.923
- Not any more.
- No, Herbert.

01:00:35.007 --> 01:00:36.175
This has gotta stop!

01:00:36.258 --> 01:00:37.801
Look, he tried
to blackmail me, Dan.

01:00:37.885 --> 01:00:38.802
Enough is enough!

01:00:38.886 --> 01:00:40.512
And he wanted you to disappear!

01:00:50.898 --> 01:00:54.652
Oh. Oh.

01:00:54.735 --> 01:00:56.362
Oh, that's why he did
it to Halsey.

01:00:56.445 --> 01:00:57.696
What? You've seen Halsey?

01:00:57.780 --> 01:01:00.949
He lobotomized him, so he could
control him in case

01:01:01.033 --> 01:01:03.285
he ever tried to talk or tell
somebody what happened.

01:01:03.369 --> 01:01:05.663
<i>So he could protect his discovery.</i>

01:01:05.704 --> 01:01:07.414
- Yes.
- Very clever.

01:01:07.498 --> 01:01:09.041
I gotta tell Meg.

01:01:09.124 --> 01:01:11.001
What does Meg
have to do with this?

01:01:11.085 --> 01:01:12.419
Hill's got this weird file on her,

01:01:12.503 --> 01:01:15.005
it's full of napkins and hair
and photographs.

01:01:15.089 --> 01:01:17.549
I think he's projected some sort
of psychotic need onto her.

01:02:55.773 --> 01:02:58.776
Yes.

01:03:13.040 --> 01:03:15.959
Alan.

01:03:22.257 --> 01:03:25.844
Alan.

01:03:55.916 --> 01:03:59.962
Oh... yes...

01:04:01.421 --> 01:04:03.549
Alan.

01:04:05.843 --> 01:04:10.848
It's... time for you...

01:04:10.931 --> 01:04:14.643
to come out now.

01:04:47.217 --> 01:04:49.177
Is that you, Dr. Hill?

01:04:49.261 --> 01:04:50.554
Of course it's me.

01:05:03.108 --> 01:05:05.193
Break time.

01:05:34.056 --> 01:05:37.935
That's... better.

01:06:24.314 --> 01:06:27.985
Meg? Meg!

01:06:28.068 --> 01:06:31.446
Dan? Dan...

01:06:31.530 --> 01:06:35.033
- I was so afraid.
- What is it?

01:06:35.117 --> 01:06:37.119
What's the matter?

01:06:37.202 --> 01:06:41.373
Well... I don't know.

01:06:41.456 --> 01:06:43.500
I was just worried about you.

01:06:45.002 --> 01:06:47.254
Why?

01:06:47.337 --> 01:06:52.050
L... I just feel horrible
about everything.

01:06:55.095 --> 01:06:57.264
I guess I'm just getting paranoid.

01:07:00.934 --> 01:07:03.353
It's just...

01:07:03.437 --> 01:07:05.022
so hard to lose you.

01:07:07.691 --> 01:07:10.110
You should go away.

01:07:12.487 --> 01:07:15.365
Transfer to another school.

01:07:15.449 --> 01:07:17.451
Don't worry about me.

01:07:20.203 --> 01:07:22.414
You're the one
that should get away.

01:07:25.333 --> 01:07:26.376
Go live your life.

01:07:30.464 --> 01:07:33.216
Find somebody.

01:07:33.300 --> 01:07:35.343
I tried to hate you.

01:07:38.764 --> 01:07:41.600
I wanted so much to hate you.

01:07:46.938 --> 01:07:49.107
I love you.

01:07:51.318 --> 01:07:52.903
No! Daddy!

01:07:52.986 --> 01:07:57.324
Dr. Halsey.

01:07:57.407 --> 01:07:59.242
No, Daddy!

01:08:03.080 --> 01:08:05.457
Oh, no, Daddy!

01:08:05.540 --> 01:08:07.834
Daddy! Daddy!

01:08:21.932 --> 01:08:23.850
The door.

01:09:05.392 --> 01:09:08.019
Oh... yes.

01:09:54.191 --> 01:09:59.196
Dan? Dan?

01:09:59.279 --> 01:10:01.364
Dan?

01:10:01.448 --> 01:10:04.201
Come on.

01:10:06.661 --> 01:10:08.747
Oh, well, you'll be all right.

01:10:08.830 --> 01:10:11.208
Meg!

01:10:11.291 --> 01:10:12.500
Oh my god.

01:10:12.584 --> 01:10:14.002
Where, Herbert?

01:10:14.085 --> 01:10:16.880
He's at the hospital I imagine.
Can you stand up?

01:10:16.963 --> 01:10:18.215
Let's go.

01:10:24.137 --> 01:10:26.137
Oh... Meg.

01:11:08.265 --> 01:11:10.976
I've... always...

01:11:11.977 --> 01:11:15.563
admired your beauty, my dear.

01:11:18.191 --> 01:11:22.320
I think I've always loved you.

01:11:30.370 --> 01:11:33.415
You will love me.

01:11:40.380 --> 01:11:42.215
You will.

01:11:44.759 --> 01:11:46.511
Please!

01:11:46.594 --> 01:11:48.596
Please stop!

01:11:48.680 --> 01:11:50.307
Let me go!

01:11:50.348 --> 01:11:53.810
That's it, my dearest Meg...

01:11:53.893 --> 01:11:56.563
more passion!

01:11:59.691 --> 01:12:04.321
- Oh my god!
- Yes, my love!

01:12:05.572 --> 01:12:07.324
I must say, Dr. Hill...

01:12:07.407 --> 01:12:11.077
I'm very disappointed in you.

01:12:11.161 --> 01:12:13.663
You steal the secret
of life and death,

01:12:13.747 --> 01:12:17.000
and here you are trysting
with the bubble-headed coed,

01:12:17.083 --> 01:12:19.878
you're not even
a second-rate scientist.

01:12:19.961 --> 01:12:23.214
Mr. West.

01:12:23.340 --> 01:12:26.468
I'm actually glad to see you.

01:12:27.969 --> 01:12:32.974
It saves me the trouble
of having to send for you.

01:12:33.058 --> 01:12:35.352
You'll never get credit
for my discovery.

01:12:35.435 --> 01:12:37.062
Who's gonna believe
a talking head?

01:12:37.145 --> 01:12:38.938
Get a job in a sideshow.

01:12:39.022 --> 01:12:41.358
I wonder why

01:12:41.441 --> 01:12:45.820
an intelligent young man like yourself

01:12:47.572 --> 01:12:52.285
should make such a foolish,
fatal mistake,

01:12:52.369 --> 01:12:56.247
of coming here to challenge me.

01:12:57.248 --> 01:13:00.418
Oh... I have a plan.

01:13:00.502 --> 01:13:04.672
So do I.

01:13:21.731 --> 01:13:23.650
Let go of me!

01:13:43.753 --> 01:13:44.921
Enough!

01:13:58.768 --> 01:14:02.772
I will show you power, Mr. West!

01:14:02.856 --> 01:14:04.983
My discovery,

01:14:05.066 --> 01:14:07.902
a laser surgical drill.

01:14:07.986 --> 01:14:12.073
It makes possible a new
technique in lobotomy,

01:14:13.074 --> 01:14:17.120
which results in total mastery

01:14:17.203 --> 01:14:19.289
of the human will.

01:14:19.372 --> 01:14:22.375
Re-animated subjects

01:14:22.459 --> 01:14:25.587
have proven to be the best.

01:14:25.670 --> 01:14:29.466
They will give me power!

01:14:29.549 --> 01:14:32.802
Undreamed of power.

01:14:35.305 --> 01:14:37.182
Stay behind me.

01:14:41.728 --> 01:14:42.896
Daddy, listen to me.

01:14:42.979 --> 01:14:45.231
It's Megan, Megan!

01:14:45.315 --> 01:14:49.235
- Hill, they'll kill her!
- Then I'll give her life!

01:14:51.237 --> 01:14:53.615
Look at me!

01:15:56.803 --> 01:15:57.887
Meg, come on!

01:15:57.971 --> 01:15:59.722
Let's go! Come on!

01:15:59.806 --> 01:16:00.723
Wait!

01:16:00.807 --> 01:16:02.475
I am not through here!

01:16:02.559 --> 01:16:04.894
Megan, no!

01:16:04.978 --> 01:16:08.439
- Let me go!
- I told you, I have a theory!

01:16:08.565 --> 01:16:10.775
- Overdose!
- No!

01:17:03.286 --> 01:17:06.706
Herbert!

01:17:24.974 --> 01:17:27.894
Look out!

01:17:34.692 --> 01:17:37.445
Daddy!

01:17:46.913 --> 01:17:47.914
My notes.

01:17:49.916 --> 01:17:51.918
MY notes!

01:17:55.254 --> 01:17:57.298
Let's go.

01:18:25.702 --> 01:18:27.704
Come on!

01:19:38.024 --> 01:19:39.150
My god! Megan!

01:19:39.233 --> 01:19:40.193
Take her into number three!

01:19:40.276 --> 01:19:42.653
Bring her this way!

01:19:46.491 --> 01:19:49.952
Hurry, hurry,
she's got nothing.

01:19:50.036 --> 01:19:52.622
Activating.

01:19:52.705 --> 01:19:53.831
Air on.

01:20:00.880 --> 01:20:02.590
Somebody give me some paste!

01:20:02.673 --> 01:20:03.883
On three.

01:20:06.385 --> 01:20:07.386
Okay, everybody off.

01:20:07.470 --> 01:20:10.348
Clear.

01:20:13.726 --> 01:20:15.394
Nothing.

01:20:16.395 --> 01:20:17.980
Bringing back air.

01:20:20.942 --> 01:20:22.819
The trachea's fractured.

01:20:22.860 --> 01:20:24.195
She's fixed and dilated.

01:20:24.278 --> 01:20:26.739
No response.

01:20:31.202 --> 01:20:35.081
Cain... Cain.

01:22:14.263 --> 01:22:15.932
I love you.

